<%= content_for(:title, "About | JW") %>
<h1 class="page-header text-center">About James Williams</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <%= image_tag "me.jpg", class: 'img-responsive' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-1">

    <p class="lead">
      After spending over 6 years in the customer service industry as a leader, team player, and customer satisfaction specialist, I have started working towards
      a new career as a Full-stack developer. I am currently attending a four month programming bootcamp known as 'Epicodus', located in Portland, Oregon. I am
      learning what it is to be a ruby, javascript, and rails web developer 40 hours a week through daily pair programming challenges. I have been interested in
      computers since I first used one as a child and am very excited to finally learn the ins and outs through computer programming. You can follow along with
      my current projects on my <a href="http://www.github.com/finalfreq">Github </a> <button class="btn btn-success" id="see-references">See References</button> <button class="btn btn-warning" id="hide-references">Hide References</button>
    </p>
    <ul id="reference-list">
      <% @references.each do |reference| if @references.any? %>
        <li> <%= reference.name %>: <%= reference.email %></li>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
      <li>Mike Goren: mike@mortalwombat.net </li>
      <li>Debbie Cravey: deborah.cravey@yahoo.com </li>
      <% if current_user != nil %>
        <li> <%= link_to "Add Reference", new_user_reference_path(current_user), remote: true %> </li>
      </ul>
      <div id="add-reference">
        <%= render 'references/form' %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<h1 class="page-header text-center">Recent Projects</h1>
<% if @projects.any? %>
  <% @projects.in_groups_of(2, false).each do |projects| %>
  <div class="row clearfix">
    <% projects.each do |project| %>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="well">
          <h2 class="lead text-center"><%= link_to project.name, category_project_path(project.category_id, project) %></h2>
          <%= image_tag "program.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <% end %>
<% else %>

<p class="lead"> No recent projects at this time </p>

<% end %>
